lead_paragraph: If anyone still doubted whether the Golden State Warriors were truly going to push for a record 73 wins instead of saving energy for the playoffs, that thought should now be put to rest for good.

headline.print_headline: Warriors Embrace Chase of Wins Record More Than Playoff Rest
